                     <interp inst="t18610505-447-verdict-3" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>
                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi> 
                     <hi rend="italic">of receiving.</hi>
                  </rs>
                  <hi rend="italic">—
<rs id="t18610505-447-punishment-38" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18610505-447-punishment-38" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18610505-447-punishment-38" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>
                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def3-447-18610505 t18610505-447-punishment-38"></join>Confined Twelve Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Carpenter stated that he believed for the last twelve months the female prisoner had been in the habit of sending the boy Kilty out thieving.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Baron Channell.</hi>
